  {
    "path": "hero.subtitle",
    "source": "No more salon stress. No more flimsy press-ons. With <strong>NaiLit</strong>, you get <strong>fully custom</strong>, <strong>hand-painted</strong>, high-quality <strong>Gel-X</strong> press-on nails for every occasion.",
